'''奧斯丁·賈瑞爾·傑克森'''（{{lang-en|Austin Jarriel Jackson}}，{{bd|1987年|2月1日}}），出生在[[登頓_(德克薩斯州)|登頓]]，為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[中外野手|中外野手]]。目前為自由球員，他先前曾效力過老虎、水手、小熊、白襪、印地安人、巨人與大都會等隊。

==職業生涯==
=== 小聯盟時期 ===
傑克森是紐約洋基隊於2005年大聯盟選秀會中第8輪第259名所選中的選手，當時以80萬美金簽下合約，為第8輪選手裡面最高的簽約金<ref name=nyt060109>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/02/sports/baseball/02jackson.html |title=Austin Jackson: A Star Under Construction |access-date=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2020-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905142415/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/02/sports/baseball/02jackson.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2005－2009年，傑克森在洋基的小聯盟系統磨練，在2009年被評為洋基農場裡面頂級的選手<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hawaiiwinterbaseball.com/articles/detail/91Austin |title=Jackson Earning His (Pin)stripes in HWB |access-date=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2011-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711151818/http://www.hawaiiwinterbaseball.com/articles/detail/91Austin |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2009/267148.html |title=New York Yankees top 10 prospects |access-date=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129140500/https://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2009/267148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2009年球季結束以後，傑克森被放進洋基隊的40人名單中，避免因規則五選秀被其他球隊選走<ref>[http://yankees.lhblogs.com/2009/11/20/seven-added-to-40-man-roster Seven added to 40-man roster] {{Wayback|url=http://yankees.lhblogs.com/2009/11/20/seven-added-to-40-man-roster |date=20100305031920 }}/</ref>。

===底特律老虎===
2009年，洋基以傑克森和底特律老虎交易[[柯蒂斯·格蘭德森|柯蒂斯·格蘭德森]] <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091208&content_id=7774692&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy |title=Granderson joins Yanks in three-way trade |access-date=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212062706/http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091208&content_id=7774692&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月5日為傑克森個人在大聯盟的第一場比賽，對手為[[堪薩斯市皇家|堪薩斯市皇家]]。4月25日，傑克森從[[德州遊騎兵|德州遊騎兵]]的先發投手Colby Lewis擊出大聯盟生涯的第1發全壘打<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100425&content_id=9579612&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Jackson jacks first home run of career |access-date=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023162309/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100425&content_id=9579612&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在大聯盟的第一個月，傑克森總共擊出36支的安打，而成為大聯盟4月份表現最佳的新人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://detroit.tigers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100504&content_id=9785236&vkey=news_det&fext=.jsp&c_id=det |title=Jackson is AL Rookie of Month for April |accessdate=2010-05-06 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615103653/http://detroit.tigers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100504&content_id=9785236&vkey=news_det&fext=.jsp&c_id=det |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===西雅圖水手===
2014年7月31日，老虎、水手與光芒進行三方交易。傑克森到了水手隊、[[大衛·普萊斯|大衛·普萊斯]]到了老虎隊、[[德魯·史邁利|德魯·史邁利]]、Nick Franklin和[[威利·亞達梅斯|威利·亞達梅斯]]則到了光芒隊。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article/sea/seattle-mariners-get-austin-jackson-from-tigers-in-david-price-deal?ymd=20140731&content_id=87302606&vkey=news_sea | title = Mariners get Jackson from Tigers in Price deal | work = [[Major_League_Baseball|MLB]] | first = Greg | last = Johns | date = July 31, 2014 | accessdate = July 31, 2014 | archive-date = 2014-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808055538/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article/sea/seattle-mariners-get-austin-jackson-from-tigers-in-david-price-deal?ymd=20140731&content_id=87302606&vkey=news_sea | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2015年5月3日，傑克森在比賽中扭傷腳踝，並在隔日進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2015/05/04/seattle-mariners-austin-jackson-injury-ankle-dl|title=Mariners place CF Austin Jackson (sprained ankle) on 15-day DL|work=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|date=May 4, 2015|accessdate=May 5, 2015|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410162501/https://www.si.com/mlb/2015/05/04/seattle-mariners-austin-jackson-injury-ankle-dl|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===芝加哥小熊===
2015年8月31日，水手將傑克森交易至小熊，換來一名日後指定球員。<ref>http://www.csnchicago.com/cubs/cubs-reportedly-acquire-outfielder-austin-jackson</ref>這年他出賽136場比賽，寫下了17次盜壘成功。
===芝加哥白襪===
2016年3月6日，傑克森與白襪隊簽下了1年500萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/25506891/report-white-sox-sign-austin-jackson-to-one-year-5-million-deal|title=White Sox sign Austin Jackson to one-year, $5 million deal|website=CBS Sports|first=Mike|last=Axisa|date=March 6, 2016|accessdate=March 7, 2016|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324094049/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/25506891/report-white-sox-sign-austin-jackson-to-one-year-5-million-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過傑克森在這年從6月10日起就未再上場。8月25日，白襪隊總經理宣布傑克森將動半月板撕裂手術，而這個手術也讓傑克森整個球季提前結束。該年他僅出賽54場比賽，打擊率為2成54。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-white-sox/white-sox-rule-austin-jackson-matt-davidson-out-season|title=White Sox rule Austin Jackson, Matt Davidson out for season|date=August 25, 2016|publisher=|access-date=2020-06-01|archive-date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815203259/http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-white-sox/white-sox-rule-austin-jackson-matt-davidson-out-season|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===克里夫蘭印地安人===
2017年1月25日，傑克森以小聯盟合約加盟印地安人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Indians invite Austin Jackson to Major League camp|url=http://m.indians.mlb.com/news/article/214382428/indians-invite-austin-jackson-to-major-league-camp/|accessdate=25 January 2017|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803005340/http://m.indians.mlb.com/news/article/214382428/indians-invite-austin-jackson-to-major-league-camp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月1日，傑克森在紅襪主場接殺了[[亨利·拉米瑞茲|亨利·拉米瑞茲]]可能形成的全壘打。當時他為了接殺飛球跑了快30公尺，並且差點摔進紅襪牛棚區。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|title=Austin Jackson soars over wall to take HR away|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/245757708/indians-austin-jackson-makes-amazing-catch/|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=August 1, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808031218/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/245757708/indians-austin-jackson-makes-amazing-catch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而這個美技也被大聯盟選為2017年度的最佳防守美技。
===舊金山巨人===
2018年1月22日，傑克森與巨人簽下2年600萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Haft|first1=Chris|title=Giants find center fielder, sign free agent A-Jax|url=https://www.mlb.com/giants/news/giants-sign-free-agent-austin-jackson/c-265151328|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=January 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215173224/https://www.mlb.com/giants/news/giants-sign-free-agent-austin-jackson/c-265151328|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===紐約大都會===
2018年7月8日，巨人隊將傑克森、Cory Gearrin與小聯盟選手Jason Bahr一同交易至遊騎兵，換來一名日後指定球員與現金。不過他在3天之後就遭到球隊指定讓渡，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2018/07/rangers-acquire-austin-jackson-cory-gearrin.html|title=Rangers Acquire Austin Jackson, Cory Gearrin; Could Trade Jackson|website=MLB Trade Rumors|access-date=2020-06-01|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043250/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2018/07/rangers-acquire-austin-jackson-cory-gearrin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於7月14日被釋出。7月27日，傑克森與大都會隊簽約。他與Juan Lagares共同分擔外野工作，填補[[約尼斯·塞佩達斯|約尼斯·塞佩達斯]]的受傷空缺。這年在球隊隊長[[大衛·萊特|大衛·萊特]]的引退賽中，傑克森敲出了再見全壘打。<ref>{{cite web |title=Mets sign Austin Jackson, designate den Dekker |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/austin-jackson-signs-with-mets/c-287612078 |publisher=MLB.com |date=July 27, 2018 |access-date=2020-06-01 |archive-date=2018-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728112404/https://www.mlb.com/news/austin-jackson-signs-with-mets/c-287612078 |dead-url=no }}</ref>10月29日，他成為自由球員。

2020年4月，傑克森表示他很願意重返大聯盟，不過至今仍未有球隊給他合約。
